## Contribution envelope

```markdown
## Code Contribution Intake

Wave: [name + path under {{paths.waves}}]
Thin-slice: [TS-NNN + title]
Sprint: [file under {{paths.sprints}}]
Wave specs: [README/product-design/product-architecture/qa status]
Current code touchpoints: [capabilities/files/contracts]
Behavior impact: [changes behavior | preserves behavior | mixed]
Test posture:
- Red-first: [tests + expected red reason]
- Green-baseline: [tests/commands]
- Missing coverage: [layer + intent]
Implementation boundary: [in scope / out of scope]
Verification commands: [commands above]
```